test_large_range:
assert [23, 24] == [24]
  At index 0 diff: 23 != 24
  Left contains one more item: 24
  Full diff:
  - [24]
  + [23, 24]
test_even_range:
assert [24, 26, 28, 30, 32, 34, ...] == [48]
  At index 0 diff: 24 != 48
  Left contains 12 more items, first extra item: 26
  Full diff:
  - [48]
  + [24, 26, 28, 30, 32, 34, 36, 38, 40, 42, 44, 46, 48]
